  <brief_title>Mifepristone and Misoprostol for 2nd Trimester Termination of Pregnancy in Burkina Faso</brief_title>
  <official_title>Mifepristone and Misoprostol for 2nd Trimester Termination of Pregnancy (13-22 Weeks LMP) in Burkina Faso</official_title>
