  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to examine the effectiveness and feasibility of a
      mifepristone-misoprostol medical abortion regimen in terminating pregnancies 13-22 weeks in
      Burkina Faso.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
